title: Redfish Power Supply
agents: agent_redfish
catalog: hw/server/redfish
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors individual power supplies of Redfish devices that use
 the newer Sensor resource model. It reports manufacturer, model, firmware
 version, capacity, line input status, and health state.

discovery:
 One service is created for each power supply that is not absent or disabled.

item:
 The resource path of the power supply.
